<lb n="0006c02" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1032</head>
<lb n="0006c03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0006031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】卅帖策子第五，【乙】建久七年寫高山寺藏本</note>瑜伽蓮華部念誦法<note n="0006032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0006032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0006032"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0006c04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0006c05" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0006033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔開府…智〕三十三字－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0006033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔開府…智〕三十三字－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app word-count="33" n="0006033"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0006c06" ed="T"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0006c07" ed="T"/>正號大廣智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0006034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大興善寺＝唐北天竺【明】</note><app n="0006034"><lem>大興善寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唐北天竺</rdg></app>三藏沙門
<lb n="0006c08" ed="T"/><note n="0006035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（大廣智）＋不【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0006035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（大廣智）＋不【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0006035"><lem>不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">大廣智不</rdg></app>空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0006c09" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT20p0006c0901">初入道場。至心頂禮懺悔發願回向等已。</p>
<lb n="0006c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0006c1001">即結蓮華合掌印　兩手<note n="0006036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">指＝相【宋】</note><app n="0006036"><lem>指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">相</rdg></app>虛其掌。似未開
<lb n="0006c11" ed="T"/>芙蓉。誦一切法清淨真言。印心額喉頂上各
<lb n="0006c12" ed="T"/>一遍。即得清淨。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0006c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0006c1301" type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆&CB00085;<note n="0006037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02124;＝戍【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0006037" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB02122;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&CB02124;</rdg></app>＝戍【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0006037"><lem>&CB02122;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">戍</rdg></app>馱薩&CB00085;達<note n="0006038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝麼【明】＊</note><app n="0006038"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app><note n="0006039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑&CB00085;二合婆&CB00085;＝薩&CB00085;婆&CB00085;二合【三】【乙】，薩&CB00085;娑&CB00085;二合【甲】</note><note n="0006039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娑&CB00085;二合婆&CB00085;＝薩&CB00085;婆&CB00085;二合【宋】【元】【明】【乙】，＝薩&CB00085;娑&CB00085;二合【甲】</note><app n="0006039"><lem>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0006c14" ed="T"/>婆&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">薩&CB00085;婆&CB00085;二合</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩&CB00085;娑&CB00085;二合</rdg></app>戍度唅</p>
<lb n="0006c15" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0006c1501">然後右膝著地。蓮華合掌置於頂上。誦真言
<lb n="0006c16" ed="T"/>想禮一切諸佛菩薩本尊足。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0006c17" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0006c1701" type="dharani">唵&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>勿<note place="inline">微一<note n="0006040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">反＝切【明】下同</note><app n="0006040"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0006c18" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0006c1801">作此法已。即於一切諸佛菩薩。禮事供養皆
<lb n="0006c19" ed="T"/>悉成就。然後結<note n="0006041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">加＝跏【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0006041"><lem>加</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】">跏</rdg></app>趺坐或半<note n="0006042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">加＝跏趺【明】，跏【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0006042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">加＝跏趺【明】，＝跏【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0006042"><lem>加</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">跏趺</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">跏</rdg></app>坐。即結蓮
<lb n="0006c20" ed="T"/>華三昧耶印。兩手外相叉合<note n="0006043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">掌＝拳【乙】</note><app n="0006043"><lem>掌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">拳</rdg></app>。&CB00594;二大指二
<pb n="0007a" id="T20.1032.0007a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0007a01" ed="T"/>小指相並。呈示一切諸佛菩薩本尊。即憶本
<lb n="0007a02" ed="T"/>誓願加持攝受。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a0301" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>三<app source="0006038" type="＊"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app>耶薩怛&CB00680;
<lb n="0007a04" ed="T"/><note place="inline"><note n="0007001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二【明】</note><app n="0007001"><lem>三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">二</rdg></app>合</note></p>
<lb n="0007a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a0501">次結極喜印。准前手<note n="0007002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">勢＝契【乙】</note><app n="0007002"><lem>勢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">契</rdg></app>。但以二<note n="0007003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（手）＋中【明】</note><app n="0007003"><lem>中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">手中</rdg></app>指。<note n="0007004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔垂〕－【三】</note><note n="0007004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔垂〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0007004"><lem>垂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0007a06" ed="T"/>下於掌中。以指面相合。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007a07" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a0701" type="dharani">唵三摩耶斛素囉多薩怛&CB00680;<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0007a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a0801">次結開心印。觀二乳上。右<note n="0007005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怛字上甲本有梵字</note>怛囉<note n="0007006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合引〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007006"><lem><note place="inline">二合<note n="0007007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【明】</note><app n="0007007"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>左<note n="0007008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吒字上甲本有梵字</note>吒
<lb n="0007a09" ed="T"/>字。如戶樞。以金剛縛三掣開。以開自心猶如
<lb n="0007a10" ed="T"/>啟扇。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a1101" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吒</p>
<lb n="0007a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a1201">次結入智印。准前金剛縛。但以二大拇指屈
<lb n="0007a13" ed="T"/>入掌中。觀一肘前有白蓮花。上置<note n="0007009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惡字上甲本有梵字</note>惡字字
<lb n="0007a14" ed="T"/>有白光。流入心中住白蓮花上。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a1501" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合<note n="0007010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【明】【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0007010"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>微舍<note n="0007011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惡＝噁【明】</note><app n="0007011"><lem>惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">噁</rdg></app><note n="0007012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔急〕－【三】</note><note n="0007012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔急〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0007012"><lem><note place="inline">急</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0007a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a1601">次結閉心門印。准前縛。但以<note n="0007013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝三【甲】</note><app n="0007013"><lem>二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">三</rdg></app>頭指並<note n="0007014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拄＝柱【乙】＊</note><app n="0007014"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">柱</rdg></app>
<lb n="0007a17" ed="T"/>二大拇指節。以其印觸心。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007a18" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a1801" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合<app source="0007010" type="＊"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>母瑟知&CB00805;<note place="inline">即觀門閉</note></p>
<lb n="0007a19" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a1901">次結定印。兩手相叉仰安臍下。以二大拇指
<lb n="0007a20" ed="T"/>向上相捻。即誦入三摩地真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a2101" type="dharani">唵三摩地&CB00425;娜<note n="0007015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">彌＝弭【明】</note><app n="0007015"><lem>彌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">弭</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007a2201">次應端身正念入三摩地。舌<app source="0007014" type="＊"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">柱</rdg></app>上&CB00171;止諸攀
<lb n="0007a23" ed="T"/>緣。觀內外一切法皆無所有。若妄念多者應
<lb n="0007a24" ed="T"/>先數息。數息法從一息至七息。又從一至七
<lb n="0007a25" ed="T"/>相續不絕。心無攀緣即不須數息。深入清淨
<lb n="0007a26" ed="T"/>無所有處。即觀諸佛遍滿虛空。其身大小猶
<lb n="0007a27" ed="T"/>如胡麻具諸相好。告行者言。善男子汝觀自
<lb n="0007a28" ed="T"/>心。又觀己身遍禮佛足。白佛言世尊云何觀
<lb n="0007a29" ed="T"/>心。心何相貌。諸佛告言。善男子心相難可測
<pb n="0007b" id="T20.1032.0007b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0007b01" ed="T"/>量。授與真言密誦觀察。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007b02" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b0201" type="dharani">唵質多&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底微鄧迦嚕弭</p>
<lb n="0007b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b0301">行者密誦諦觀己心猶如淨月。諸佛告言。善
<lb n="0007b04" ed="T"/>男子汝心本如是。<note n="0007016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">但＝怛【宋】【元】</note><app n="0007016"><lem>但</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">怛</rdg></app>客塵所翳。當知此即是
<lb n="0007b05" ed="T"/>菩提心。又授真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b0601" type="dharani">唵冒地質多　<note n="0007017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">畝＝母【明】</note><app n="0007017"><lem>畝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">母</rdg></app>怛波<note place="inline">二合</note>娜夜弭</p>
<lb n="0007b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b0701">誦此真言。諦觀心月<note n="0007018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">轉＝輪【乙】</note><app n="0007018"><lem>轉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">輪</rdg></app>更分明淨無瑕翳。即
<lb n="0007b08" ed="T"/>於月輪中觀紇<note n="0007019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唎＝哩【明】</note><app n="0007019"><lem>唎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">哩</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>字。成<note n="0007020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一＝百【宋】【元】</note><app n="0007020"><lem>一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">百</rdg></app>八葉白蓮花
<lb n="0007b09" ed="T"/>光明顯照。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b1001" type="dharani">唵底瑟<note n="0007021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00109;＝吒【明】＊</note><app n="0007021"><lem>&CB00109;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">吒</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b1101">次又觀此白蓮華遍周法界量同虛空。真言
<lb n="0007b12" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0007b13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b1301" type="dharani">唵薩癹<note place="inline">二合</note>囉&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜<app source="0006038" type="＊"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b1401">次觀白蓮華漸漸收斂。虛空諸佛悉入其中
<lb n="0007b15" ed="T"/>量等己身。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b1601" type="dharani">唵僧<note n="0007022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＝賀【明】</note><app n="0007022"><lem>訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">賀</rdg></app>囉&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜<app source="0006038" type="＊"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b1701">即變蓮華成觀自在菩薩。寶冠瓔珞相好莊嚴。
<lb n="0007b18" ed="T"/>放大光明遍周法界。冠上有無量壽佛本尊
<lb n="0007b19" ed="T"/>左手執白蓮花。右手作擘開蓮華勢。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b2001" type="dharani">唵三摩喻<note n="0007023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">含＝舍【甲】</note><app n="0007023"><lem>含</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">舍</rdg></app><app source="0006038" type="＊"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app>訶三摩喻含薩婆怛<note n="0007024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">他孽＝多孽【明】，他&CB00617;【乙】</note><note n="0007024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他孽＝多孽【明】，＝他&CB00617;【乙】</note><app n="0007024"><lem>他孽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">多孽</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">他&CB00617;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0007b21" ed="T"/><note n="0007025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">多＝多引【宋】【元】，哆【明】</note><note n="0007025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多＝多引【宋】【元】，＝哆【明】</note><app n="0007025"><lem>多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">多引</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">哆</rdg></app>毘三冒地&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜<note n="0007026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝麼【三】</note><note n="0007026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩＝麼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0007026"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">麼</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>阿怛
<lb n="0007b22" ed="T"/><app source="0006038" type="＊"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>句含</p>
<lb n="0007b23" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b2301">入是三昧者。一切天龍八部。見行者身與觀
<lb n="0007b24" ed="T"/>自在等無差別。能除行者無量億劫生死重
<lb n="0007b25" ed="T"/>罪。一切勝願無不悉<note n="0007027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">地＝成【宋】【元】，備【明】</note><note n="0007027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">地＝成【宋】【元】，＝備【明】</note><app n="0007027"><lem>地</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">成</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">備</rdg></app>。現得圓滿金剛法
<lb n="0007b26" ed="T"/>身。即觀此身便成正覺。</p>
<lb n="0007b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007b2701">次結加持印。外相叉金剛<note n="0007028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">縛結＝結縛【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0007028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縛結＝結縛【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007028"><lem>縛結</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">結縛</rdg></app>已。即變屈二
<lb n="0007b28" ed="T"/>頭指。捻二大拇指。印心額喉頂各誦一遍。真
<lb n="0007b29" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<pb n="0007c" id="T20.1032.0007c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0007c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c0101" type="dharani">唵紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note>薩婆迦哩阿地瑟<app source="0007021" type="＊"><lem>&CB00109;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">吒</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0007c02" ed="T"/>合</note>&CB00805;</p>
<lb n="0007c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c0301">次結灌頂印。合掌已。&CB00594;二大拇指。偃<note n="0007029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蹙＝戚【乙】</note><app n="0007029"><lem>蹙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">戚</rdg></app>八
<lb n="0007c04" ed="T"/>指如寶形。置於頂上誦真言三遍。想五如來
<lb n="0007c05" ed="T"/>冠以冠其首。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007c06" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c0601" type="dharani">唵紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note>摩抳&CB00425;娜<app source="0006038" type="＊"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>阿毘詵者薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0007c07" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;怛<note n="0007030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00080;＝&CB02255;【三】【甲】，洛【乙】</note><note n="0007030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00080;＝&CB02255;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】，＝洛【乙】</note><app n="0007030"><lem>&CB00080;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&CB02255;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">洛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007c08" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c0801">次結繫鬘印誦真言。以前冠頂印。從<note n="0007031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">額＝頭【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007031"><lem>額</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">頭</rdg></app>分
<lb n="0007c09" ed="T"/>二手。於腦後三相繞如繫鬘。便向前耳邊下。
<lb n="0007c10" ed="T"/>從小指散垂如鬘帶勢。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c1101" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜<app source="0006038" type="＊"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0007032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">磨＝麼【明】</note><app n="0007032"><lem>磨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app>隸&CB00805;紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007c12" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c1201">次結甲冑印。結金剛拳如小兒握固。以二頭
<lb n="0007c13" ed="T"/>指各<app source="0007014" type="＊"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">柱</rdg></app>二大拇指節。當心已。即伸二頭指相
<lb n="0007c14" ed="T"/>掩一節許。仍以右<note n="0007033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">指＋（押）【三】</note><note n="0007033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">指＋（押）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0007033"><lem>指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">指押</rdg></app>左指上。觀右頭指面有
<lb n="0007c15" ed="T"/>唵字。左頭指面有<note n="0007034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跕＝砧【三】</note><note n="0007034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">跕＝砧【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0007034"><lem>跕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">砧</rdg></app>字。口中仍誦此兩字真
<lb n="0007c16" ed="T"/>言不斷絕。想其字並放綠色光。如抽藕絲光
<lb n="0007c17" ed="T"/>不斷絕。心前三繞。<note n="0007035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔背上三繞〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007035"><lem>背上三繞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>。又至臍又至
<lb n="0007c18" ed="T"/>兩膝。又至腰又當心。次右肩左肩次至額上。
<lb n="0007c19" ed="T"/>又於腦後各<note n="0007036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＋（遍）【明】</note><app n="0007036"><lem>三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">三遍</rdg></app>繞已。&CB00230;結金剛拳印從小指
<lb n="0007c20" ed="T"/>散如垂天衣。</p>
<lb n="0007c21" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c2101">即以二縛不得解。但以掌三相拍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c2201" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜<app source="0006038" type="＊"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00418;<note n="0007037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">史＝使【明】</note><app n="0007037"><lem>史</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">使</rdg></app>也<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0007038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">斛＋（引）細註【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0007038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斛＋（引）細註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007038"><lem>斛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">斛<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0007c23" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c2301">次於壇中觀阿<note n="0007039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＋（聲）【明】，〔上〕－【甲】</note><app n="0007039"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">上聲</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>字成月輪。於月輪中觀紇
<lb n="0007c24" ed="T"/>唎<note n="0007040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007040"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>字成本尊身。放大光明。無量眷屬普
<lb n="0007c25" ed="T"/>現於圓光內。</p>
<lb n="0007c26" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c2601">即結鉤印。金剛縛舉右頭指。如鉤三招。一誦
<lb n="0007c27" ed="T"/>一招。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0007c28" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c2801" type="dharani">唵阿夜係弱</p>
<lb n="0007c29" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0007c2901"><note n="0007041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次＋（結）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007041"><lem>次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">次結</rdg></app>以索印。如前縛以二頭指相<app source="0007014" type="＊"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">柱</rdg></app>如環。引
<pb n="0008a" id="T20.1032.0008a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0008a01" ed="T"/>本尊入所觀智身。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a0201" type="dharani">唵阿係吽吽</p>
<lb n="0008a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a0301">次結鎖印。准前縛以二頭指及二<note n="0008001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大〕－【甲】</note><app n="0008001"><lem>大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>指。相串
<lb n="0008a04" ed="T"/>各相捻如聯鎖。令本尊止住。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a0501" type="dharani">唵係薩普<note n="0008002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二合吒&CB00805;＝吒二合&CB00680;【三】，吒三合&CB00805;【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0008002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合吒&CB00805;＝吒二合&CB00680;【宋】【元】【明】，＝吒三合&CB00805;【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008002"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note>吒&CB00805;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">吒二合&CB00680;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">吒三合&CB00805;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0008a06" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a0601">次結鈴印。准前縛屈二大拇指入掌中。三撼
<lb n="0008a07" ed="T"/>手如搖鈴。令本尊歡喜。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a0801" type="dharani">唵尾舍耶斛<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0008a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a0901">次結獻<note n="0008003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遏＝閼【明】</note><app n="0008003"><lem>遏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">閼</rdg></app>伽香水印。誦百字真言或餘讚歎。
<lb n="0008a10" ed="T"/>兩手外相叉擘開掌。以二中指頭相合。以二
<lb n="0008a11" ed="T"/>頭指微屈。去中指<note n="0008004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔背〕－【三】</note><note n="0008004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔背〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0008004"><lem>背</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>一麥許不相著。狀如
<lb n="0008a12" ed="T"/>三鈷杵頭。二大拇指博著二頭指下側。即想
<lb n="0008a13" ed="T"/>香水滿掬。誦真言向前寫灌洗本尊足。真言
<lb n="0008a14" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0008a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a1501" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日<note n="0008005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00080;＝路【宋】【元】【甲】</note><app n="0008005"><lem>&CB00080;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】">路</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>娜迦<note n="0008006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">坼＝吒【明】</note><app n="0008006"><lem>坼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">吒</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0008a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a1601">本尊既至次結羯<note n="0008007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝磨【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0008007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩＝磨【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008007"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">磨</rdg></app>印。左手金剛拳當心著。
<lb n="0008a17" ed="T"/>想把白蓮華。右手亦金剛拳於上轉。想撥開
<lb n="0008a18" ed="T"/>蓮<note n="0008008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">葉＝華【三】</note><note n="0008008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">葉＝華【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0008008"><lem>葉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">華</rdg></app>即身。同本尊事業真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008a19" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a1901" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>達<app source="0006038" type="＊"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app>紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0008a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a2001">次結三昧耶印。金剛縛屈二頭指。以二大拇
<lb n="0008a21" ed="T"/>指押。同已上加持印。令本尊憶<note n="0008009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">本＋（尊）【乙】</note><app n="0008009"><lem>本</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">本尊</rdg></app>誓願加持
<lb n="0008a22" ed="T"/>攝護。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a2301" type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;迦<note n="0008010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">里＝哩【明】</note><app n="0008010"><lem>里</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">哩</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0008011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誦三遍＝三遍誦【宋】【元】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008011"><lem>誦三遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】【乙】">三遍誦</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0008a24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a2401">然後結金剛嬉戲內供養印。金剛縛伸二大
<lb n="0008a25" ed="T"/>拇指。偃向身相並當心。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008a26" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a2601" type="dharani">唵摩訶囉底<note place="inline">丁以反</note></p>
<lb n="0008a27" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a2701">次結鬘。准前印更不改。但以二<note n="0008012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">臂＝擘【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008012"><lem>臂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">擘</rdg></app>相並直
<lb n="0008a28" ed="T"/>伸。向前當額。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008a2901" type="dharani">唵<note n="0008013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00080;＝&CB02255;【宋】【元】</note><app n="0008013"><lem>&CB00080;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">&CB02255;</rdg></app>波輸<note n="0008014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陛＝階【甲】</note><app n="0008014"><lem>陛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">階</rdg></app></p>
<pb n="0008b" id="T20.1032.0008b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0008b01" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b0101">次結歌印。不改前印。從前至口解散。向前垂
<lb n="0008b02" ed="T"/>二手下。如發歌音。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b0301" type="dharani">唵&CB02122;<note n="0008015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚧＝&CB02828;【甲】</note><app n="0008015"><lem>嚧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB02828;</rdg></app><note place="inline">上輸律反下縷音二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>燥溪</p>
<lb n="0008b04" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b0401">次結舞印。以二金剛拳相旋繞。各從小指散。
<lb n="0008b05" ed="T"/>便金剛合掌置於頂上<note place="inline">金剛合掌者合掌令指頭右押左頭相交<note n="0008016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔是也〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008016"><lem>是也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>真
<lb n="0008b06" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b0701" type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;布<note n="0008017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">而＝逝【明】</note><app n="0008017"><lem>而</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">逝</rdg></app><note place="inline">而曳反</note>　已上<note n="0008018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">內四＝四內【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0008018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">內四＝四內【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008018"><lem>內四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">四內</rdg></app>供養</p>
<lb n="0008b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b0801">次結焚香印。以金剛縛向下<note n="0008019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">解散＝散解【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008019"><lem>解散</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">散解</rdg></app>。如焚香。
<lb n="0008b09" ed="T"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b1001" type="dharani">唵&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>訶囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;寧<note place="inline"><note n="0008020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＋（聲）【明】</note><app n="0008020"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app>引</note></p>
<lb n="0008b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b1101">次結華印。以金剛縛向上解散。如散華。真言
<lb n="0008b12" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0008b13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b1301" type="dharani">唵頗&CB00256;&CB00344;弭</p>
<lb n="0008b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b1401">次結燈印。准前嬉戲。但以二大拇指。頭屈前
<lb n="0008b15" ed="T"/>相逼。亦不得相著指。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b1601" type="dharani">唵素帝惹<note n="0008021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">仡＝紇【乙】</note><app n="0008021"><lem>仡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">紇</rdg></app>哩<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0008b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b1701">次結塗香印。以金剛縛解散。摩胸上如塗香
<lb n="0008b18" ed="T"/>勢真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b1901" type="dharani">唵素<note n="0008022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">巘＝&CB03306;【宋】【元】，喭【明】</note><note n="0008022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">巘＝&CB03306;【宋】【元】，＝喭【明】</note><app n="0008022"><lem>巘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">&CB03306;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">喭</rdg></app>蕩儗<note place="inline">妍以反</note>　已上外四供養</p>
<lb n="0008b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008b2001">次結部心根本印。合掌以二<note n="0008023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔無〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008023"><lem>無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>名指二頭指。
<lb n="0008b21" ed="T"/>初分相交。其二小指二大拇指擘開。誦百字
<lb n="0008b22" ed="T"/>真言三遍。三字半七遍已於頂上散。然後
<lb n="0008b23" ed="T"/>執念珠念誦。二手把珠當心念誦。諦觀本
<lb n="0008b24" ed="T"/>尊放淨光明。流注已頂照於心月。月有白
<lb n="0008b25" ed="T"/>蓮華。身與本尊色相無二。如<note n="0008024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">於＝有【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008024"><lem>於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">有</rdg></app>明鏡自觀
<lb n="0008b26" ed="T"/>己身。與本尊互成影像。遍數終<note n="0008025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訖＝說【甲】</note><app n="0008025"><lem>訖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">說</rdg></app>懺悔發
<lb n="0008b27" ed="T"/>願。重獻三昧耶重結八供養。然後發遣聖者
<lb n="0008b28" ed="T"/>復還本宮。發遣者用前三昧耶印當口解。真
<pb n="0008c" id="T20.1032.0008c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0008c01" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008c0201" type="dharani">唵&CB00425;娜<app source="0006038" type="＊"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>薩怛<note n="0008026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">縛＝&CB00085;【三】【甲】</note><note n="0008026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縛＝&CB00085;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0008026"><lem>縛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&CB00085;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>穆<note place="inline"><note n="0008027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">輕＋（呼）【明】</note><app n="0008027"><lem>輕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">輕呼</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0008c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008c0301">然後<note n="0008028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔復〕－【甲】</note><app n="0008028"><lem>復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>結加持灌頂甲冑拍印等。然後出道
<lb n="0008c04" ed="T"/>場。或讀大乘經。或印佛作塔。於一切時本尊
<lb n="0008c05" ed="T"/>三<note n="0008029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝麼【乙】</note><app n="0008029"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">麼</rdg></app>地不令間斷。若觸穢處當觀頂上有法
<lb n="0008c06" ed="T"/>界生字。<note n="0008030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">放＝於【宋】【元】</note><app n="0008030"><lem>放</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">於</rdg></app>赤色光。所謂&CB00771;字。於所食物皆
<lb n="0008c07" ed="T"/>加持此字。即不成穢觸於一切供養香華。皆
<lb n="0008c08" ed="T"/>加<note n="0008031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔持〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008031"><lem>持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>此字放白色光。即無穢觸。所供養物
<lb n="0008c09" ed="T"/>皆遍法界。</p>
<lb n="0008c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008c1001">蓮華<note n="0008032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔部〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0008032"><lem>部</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">&lac;</rdg></app>百字真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0008c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0008c1101" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00425;娜<note n="0008033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝麼【明】，磨【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0008033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩＝麼【明】，＝磨【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008033"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">磨</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合<note n="0008034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔下同〕－【明】＊</note><app n="0008034"><lem>下同</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<app source="0008034" type="＊"><lem>下同</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>三<note n="0008035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩耶二摩努＝麼耶三麼弩【宋】，麼耶二麼弩【元】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0008035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩耶二摩努＝麼耶三麼弩【宋】，＝麼耶二麼弩【元】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008035"><lem>摩耶<note place="inline">二</note><app source="0006038" type="＊"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">麼</rdg></app>
<lb n="0008c12" ed="T"/><note n="0008036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">努＝怒【明】</note><app n="0008036"><lem>努</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">怒</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">麼耶三麼弩</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【甲】【乙】">麼耶二麼弩</rdg></app>播羅耶<note place="inline">三</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合四</note>怛尾弩
<lb n="0008c13" ed="T"/>波底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合五</note>涅<note n="0008037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">哩＝里【宋】【元】【甲】</note><app n="0008037"><lem>哩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】">里</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>住<note n="0008038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔茶護反〕－【明】，茶＝荼【甲】</note><app n="0008038"><lem><note place="inline">茶護反</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">荼護反</note></rdg></app>銘婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">六</note>素&CB00418;
<lb n="0008c14" ed="T"/>使諭<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0008039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寐＝銘【明】＊</note><app n="0008039"><lem>寐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">銘</rdg></app>婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">七</note>阿弩囉訖&CB00418;<note place="inline">二合</note><app source="0008039" type="＊"><lem>寐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">銘</rdg></app>婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">八</note>
<lb n="0008c15" ed="T"/>素補使諭<anchor id="fxT20p0008c05"/><note place="inline">二合</note><app source="0008039" type="＊"><lem>寐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">銘</rdg></app>婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">九</note>薩&CB00085;悉地寐&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0008c16" ed="T"/>合</note>也<note n="0008040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瑳＝縒【明】</note><app n="0008040"><lem>瑳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">縒</rdg></app><note place="inline">十</note>薩&CB00085;羯磨素者<app source="0008039" type="＊"><lem>寐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">銘</rdg></app><note place="inline">十一</note>質多室唎<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0008c17" ed="T"/>合</note>藥<note place="inline">十二</note>句<note n="0008041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00080;＝盧【明】</note><app n="0008041"><lem>&CB00080;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">盧</rdg></app>吽<note place="inline">十三</note>呵呵呵呵<note n="0008042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">穀＝斛【明】</note><app n="0008042"><lem>穀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">斛</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0008043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">十四引＝引十四【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0008043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十四引＝引十四【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008043"><lem>十四引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">引十四</rdg></app></note>薄伽
<lb n="0008c18" ed="T"/>梵<note place="inline">十五</note>薩&CB00085;怛他<note n="0008044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">孽＝&CB00344;【明】，&CB00617;【乙】</note><note n="0008044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">孽＝&CB00344;【明】，＝&CB00617;【乙】</note><app n="0008044"><lem>孽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&CB00344;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&CB00617;</rdg></app>多<note place="inline">十六</note>&CB00425;娜<note n="0008045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麼＝摩【宋】【元】</note><app n="0008045"><lem>麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">摩</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合十七</note>麼寐
<lb n="0008c19" ed="T"/><note n="0008046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悶＝門【明】</note><app n="0008046"><lem>悶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">門</rdg></app>者<note place="inline">十八</note>&CB00425;娜<app source="0008039" type="＊"><lem>寐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">銘</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">十九</note>摩訶三<note n="0008047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝麼【乙】</note><app n="0008047"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">麼</rdg></app>耶薩
<lb n="0008c20" ed="T"/>怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合二十</note>紇唎<note place="inline">二合<note n="0008048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引聲＝二十一【明】</note><app n="0008048"><lem>引<note n="0008049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">聲＋（二十一）細註【宋】【元】</note><app n="0008049"><lem>聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">聲<note place="inline">二十一</note></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">二十一</rdg></app></note></p>
